sellerCard.description:
I love to dig into customer problems and solve them with modern technology. I create, scale, and optimize business portfolios that matter. To accomplish this, I focus on delivering key outcomes, building amazing teams, and quickly adapting to new learnings.

I have enjoyed many business domains throughout my career including Medical, Grocery Delivery, E-Commerce, On-Demand Booking Services, and Educational apps.

I can successfully scale up software businesses from 1 user to 1 million. - I put the customer at the center of all that I do.

description.content:
Greetings


If you are looking for someone to create professional responsive website in reactjs and nodejs with reasonable budget then you are at the right place.I am an experienced React JS developer expert in developing user-friendly websites. I can develop any kind of web app that fits your needs and business requirements.


Expertise in:


  •    React JS
  •    Redux
  •    React Material UI
  •    Bootstrap 4
  •    Rest API Integration
  •    Node JS
  • Express JS
  •    Mongo DB
  •    Build Restful API's


Benefits you'll have:

  1. Fully documented source code.
  2. Project delivery within the deadline
  3. Deployment on cheap servers (Heroku)



Kindly Contact me before Placing your Order.


Warm Regards,

Waleed Saifi
